    "description": "The SonicWALL TZ 170 is an internet security appliance with a WAN interface, a flexible Optional interface, and a LAN interface incorporating a 5-port Fast-Ethernet switch. The SonicWALL TZ 170 provides stateful packet inspection firewall services, accelerated IPSec VPN, bandwidth management, and can be upgraded to offer ISP failover and traffic loadbalancing. The SonicWALL TZ 170 also serves as a platform for extensible security services such as Content Filtering Services (CFS), Network Anti - Virus, and E-mail filtering.",
